categories.title: First Contentful Paint
categories.description: First Contentful Paint marks the time at which the first text or image is painted. [Learn more](https://web.dev/first-contentful-paint/).

categories.title: Speed Index
categories.description: Speed Index shows how quickly the contents of a page are visibly populated. [Learn more](https://web.dev/speed-index/).

categories.title: Largest Contentful Paint
categories.description: Largest Contentful Paint marks the time at which the largest text or image is painted. [Learn more](https://web.dev/lighthouse-largest-contentful-paint/)

categories.title: Time to Interactive
categories.description: Time to interactive is the amount of time it takes for the page to become fully interactive. [Learn more](https://web.dev/interactive/).

categories.title: Total Blocking Time
categories.description: Sum of all time periods between FCP and Time to Interactive, when task length exceeded 50ms, expressed in milliseconds. [Learn more](https://web.dev/lighthouse-total-blocking-time/).

categories.title: Cumulative Layout Shift
categories.description: Cumulative Layout Shift measures the movement of visible elements within the viewport. [Learn more](https://web.dev/cls/).
